beliefs or thoughts

00:47:43.390 --> 00:47:46.420
about monsters, physical
abnormalities,

00:47:46.420 --> 00:47:47.720
and bizarre animals.

00:47:47.720 --> 00:47:51.140
And so, again, I see this
as a kind of, you know --

00:47:51.140 --> 00:47:53.910
it's located in the
Rare Book Room.

00:47:53.910 --> 00:47:56.950
It's an illustration of
this evolving imagination

00:47:56.950 --> 00:48:01.310
