00:48:29.430 --> 00:48:32.330
most of Bois-Regard's work is
interested in this [inaudible],

00:48:32.330 --> 00:48:37.100
is interested in preventing and
correcting poor body posture

00:48:37.100 --> 00:48:38.510
and other defects caused

00:48:38.510 --> 00:48:41.030
by improper habits during
children's formative years;

00:48:41.030 --> 00:48:43.520
As you can, I think see,
