00:49:06.580 --> 00:49:10.150
there is this ongoing interest
in defining and categorizing

00:49:10.150 --> 00:49:15.670
and uncovering an understanding
of our place in the world.

00:49:15.670 --> 00:49:17.810
And I think that's
imaginative in nature.

